{"tid":864903,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"放工/放學返到屋企好攰  點先唔會比屋企人煩?","createTime":"2018-10-16T14:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T08:29:59.000Z","uid":13138,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e79a15daf3d5f309c7c137694b01be3de66a517c","tid":864903,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"講下背景 屋企好細 我阿媽一講野又可以自己講成幾個鐘 咩野都有排講 罵罵下我老豆都可以罵埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時收工返歸仲要聽佢講自己幾慘真係人都癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大佬呀我上司直頭唔當我係人tim啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n最近學到一招 就係成日扮到好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講d悔氣說話比佢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢一開始咿咿哦哦就同佢講: 你咁嘈我聽朝點夠精神做野又或者話佢搞到自己精神彷彿/就黎痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   聽朝返工唔夠精神比車碌死架啦....<br />\n<br />\n如果你份工有危險性質你仲可以放大黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廚房佬就話唔記得熄火炸撚死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 地盤佬就話唔記得帶安全帶跌撚死/觸電死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間唔中send d年輕人自殺新聞比佢睇 再加多句「條友比車碌到散曬  哈哈... 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我依家遲左收工 阿媽會wtsapp我洗唔洗留餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一返到屋企佢就自己靜靜地睇電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好幸福呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4becfbcf2f68a443262b3848ad09953c6d09bd","tid":864903,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"搬走"},{"pid":"fe75d8fcc4c3488c00ed0942d2accc0e2c5e3f15","tid":864903,"uid":19667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"fa881dca01172642003b432e0211